method is called when the user taps on the body of the callout view, as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"opposed to the callout’s left or right accessory view. If the annotation has a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"custom callout view via the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method, this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method is only called whenever the callout view calls its delegate’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutViewDelegate\/calloutViewTapped:","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If this method is present on the delegate, the standard callout view’s body","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"momentarily highlights when the user taps it, whether or not this method does","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"anything in response to the tap.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples","level":4},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Display custom views as callouts, learn how to trigger an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"action when an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":"s "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" is tapped."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped on an annotation’s callout view."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:taponcalloutforannotation:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped on an annotation’s callout view."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:taponcalloutforannotation:","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNCalloutViewDelegate/calloutViewTapped:":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"calloutViewTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncalloutviewdelegate\/calloutviewtapped:","title":"calloutViewTapped:","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"calloutViewTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the callout view has been tapped."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutViewDelegate\/calloutViewTapped:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","role":"symbol","title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"},{"text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"require the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","title":"MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}]}}}